### Function Signatures
```python
from typing import Any, Dict, List, Optional, Union

def process(
    data: Union[str, Dict[str, Any]],
    options: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None
) -> Dict[str, Any]:
    ...
```

### Class Attributes
```python
class MyClass:
    name: str
    config: Dict[str, Any]
    
    def __init__(self, name: str) -> None:
        self.name = name
```
